column5: Haven't seen something this cool in a while
on temagami we pull our baits away from trout that size while waiting for the big ones to bite       still waiting....
LOL Terry... just to bad we have to wait 'till the 15th of Feb to play that game...  THANKS Paul !
nice!
WWWWOOOOOWWWWW!!!!! Thanks for that one, Paul
Cool vid, I catch brookies that fat,one time had a 8lb brookie at the hole but the hole was way to small he ended up breaking off!!  There is always next weekend!Damn brookies aint getting away then!
Kinda like the splake I'm waiting for enough ice to go after.  I love pulling fish like that up on a hand line. When you set the hook...OMG
Wicked Thanks for sharing Paul!!! Leechman
thanks for posting that ....   i love ice fishing for lakers ....  best ice fishing video I have ever seen ..... hands down ...
Oh my.....what a tank!
well close
Nice laker Terry!
yeah Irishfield/Wayne caught it and is king of temgami lake trout   I just shoot videos and wait for my turn  and wait  and wait
I thought it was the one you caught that won first place in the Fishing for Tyler Event...
nice fishes!!
yeah but that's simcoe anyone with a bent safety-pin and a string can catch them there   LOL
Fish God's are just testing your patience Terry!
Ya gotta love the ice clarity in that video   ... BEAUTY Laker as well!!   RFS
I just about flipped out on them once  almost....LOL
